        <mxCell id="rules" parent="1" style="shape=note;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;size=18;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=10;spacingTop=8;fontSize=13;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#666666;" value="&lt;b&gt;Business rules&lt;/b&gt;&lt;hr/&gt;Delivery-note reading stores count evidence in UploadBatchLine. Users do not manually edit quantity.&lt;br/&gt;Applying a delivery note creates an InventoryPublication and InventoryStatusChange rows only for products whose derived status changed.&lt;br/&gt;Manual product-card status changes create InventoryStatusChange rows with publicationId = NULL.&lt;br/&gt;Products absent from a delivery note are not converted to SOLD_OUT by publication." vertex="1">
